      <title>英国需要现金。财政大臣里夫斯可以发挥创意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/how-uk-chancellor-reeves-could-get-creative-on-budget-rules-to-raise-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于多年投资不足和税收负担达到二战后的最高水平，英国公共服务陷入困境，财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯警告称，她面临着平衡国家财政的“艰难决定”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/how-uk-chancellor-reeves-could-get-creative-on-budget-rules-to-raise-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>糖和咖啡价格下跌，因交易商关注巴西降雨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/sugar-and-coffee-fall-as-traders-focus-on-rains-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[咖啡和原糖期货价格在本月上涨后出现回落，原因是下周最大出口国巴西将迎来降雨，有望帮助农作物生长，这给咖啡和原糖期货价格带来了一些缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/sugar-and-coffee-fall-as-traders-focus-on-rains-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
