      <title>Steward Health 首席执行官就藐视法庭的裁决起诉参议院委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/steward-health-ceo-sues-senate-committee-over-contempt-finding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉尔夫·德拉托雷 (Ralph de la Torre) 是陷入破产的 Steward Health Care System 的首席执行官兼创始人，他起诉了正在调查该医院连锁店财务崩溃的美国参议院委员会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/steward-health-ceo-sues-senate-committee-over-contempt-finding</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cineworld 英国重组计划获伦敦法院批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/cineworld-uk-restructuring-plan-given-blessing-by-london-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管遭到部分连锁影院业主的反对，Cineworld 英国分公司通过重组大幅削减租金的计划还是得到了伦敦一名法官的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/cineworld-uk-restructuring-plan-given-blessing-by-london-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险上升，私人贷款机构发行高等级债券数量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/private-lenders-raise-most-high-grade-debt-ever-as-risks-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年私人信贷领域的巨头们筹集了史上最多的投资级债务，与此同时，他们的现金已达到创纪录的水平，并且正在努力保持与竞争对手银行的竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/private-lenders-raise-most-high-grade-debt-ever-as-risks-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:11:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DirecTV 收购 Dish，打造美国付费电视巨头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/megadeal-forges-pay-tv-giant-in-era-when-streaming-rules-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DirecTV 和 Dish 已同意合并，这将创造美国最大的付费电视提供商，拥有约 1800 万用户。这项合并已被讨论多年，参与的参与者众多。彭博社的 Crystal Tse 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/megadeal-forges-pay-tv-giant-in-era-when-streaming-rules-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:04:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织承诺支持孟加拉国改革以实现经济稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/imf-pledges-to-support-bangladesh-reforms-for-economic-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织承诺与孟加拉国临时政府合作，恢复经济稳定，因为该国正努力减轻外汇储备压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/imf-pledges-to-support-bangladesh-reforms-for-economic-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国联邦贸易委员会称，赫斯首席执行官与欧佩克的沟通导致其失去雪佛龙董事会资格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/ftc-cites-opec-communication-in-barring-hess-from-chevron-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国监管机构将允许雪佛龙公司推进其以 530 亿美元收购赫斯公司的计划，但禁止首席执行官约翰赫斯加入该超级巨头的董事会，称他与欧佩克进行了不当沟通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/ftc-cites-opec-communication-in-barring-hess-from-chevron-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 14:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
