      <title>飓风海伦导致家禽养殖场停工，棉花作物受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/hurricane-helene-halts-poultry-plants-damages-pecan-trees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风海伦导致鸡肉加工厂停工，对一些鸡群造成严重破坏，洪水淹没了美国南部，还刮倒了山核桃树，夷平了棉花作物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/hurricane-helene-halts-poultry-plants-damages-pecan-trees</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 02:23:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
